    <div id="body">
     <p id="pagetitle">
      Welcome to the Central Policy Web Site
     </p>
     <p id="pagenote">
      This is the official web site for UC Berkeley administrative policies.
     </p>
     <p id="pagenote">
      The purpose of the web site is to make our policies and procedures widely accessible and to increase individual and departmental compliance. Administrative policies may be issued by The Board of Regents, the Office of the President, or the campus. Policies from all three sources are included.
     </p>
     <p id="pagenote">
      For more information, please contact the Campus Policy Coordinator at
      <a href="mailto:ucbpolicy@berkeley.edu">
       ucbpolicy@berkeley.edu
      </a>
      .
     </p>
